From: courtney hook courtneyhook(-at-)shaw.ca
Linda that carb is a two barrel downdraft carb really designed for inline 4's
and modified for Type 4 engines. Your 1600 would not be a good match for this
really. If you are using a stock dual port 1600 Type 1 engine then I would
suggest you stick to the stock 34pict Solex carb that was used on the 1600.
